divs: Sighting DetailsA friend of mine that lives with me likes to brouse web cams and found these pics. I had him send me a few because they were interesting! Whatever this thing is seems to be moving away from the camera in a SW direction. I posted these pics on web site, and someone magnified it. There's something Strange there? When I first saw thease pics, I thought there was a good chance this thing is nothing, but after one of the pic were magnified, I'm not so sure what it is...
Summary: This was filmed on a new station web cam
